# Raw transcript artefacts before they are reviewed and promoted into
# docs/live-proof/. Keep raw outputs out of git; only the sanitized,
# pin-stamped copy under docs/live-proof/ is committed.
evidence/

# Codex CLI worker scratch dirs (operator-side; never commit)
# Workers occasionally write run artefacts here; keep them out of the SDK delivery.
.codex-runs/

# Daybook orchestration content that does NOT belong in the SDK delivery.
# Workers have repeatedly leaked these files into the repo despite explicit
# prompts; ignoring them by default makes scope leaks self-healing.
WORKTREES.md
scripts/agent/
# If copied to repo root by mistake (canonical: ~/Downloads + daybook sync).
/JOURNAL.md
/LESSONS.md

